President Trump and Prime Minister Modi of India have met at the Sofitel Philippine Plaza Manila. President Trump congratulated Prime Minister Modi on his efforts to bring factions in India together. They discussed the growing relations between India and the United States, emphasizing that they are not just for mutual interests but also for the future of Asia and humanity. President Trump expressed his high opinion of India during his recent travels, and Prime Minister Modi assured him that India will continue to fulfill the expectations of the world and the United States.